    <content>
      <![CDATA[<p>TypeScript 的类型系统是其最强大的特性之一。本文将带你探索一些高级类型技巧。</p><h2 id="泛型约束"><a href="#泛型约束" class="headerlink" title="泛型约束"></a>泛型约束</h2><p>限制泛型必须包含某些属性：</p><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">interface</span> <span class="title class_">HasLength</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">length</span>: <span class="built_in">number</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">function</span> logLength&lt;T <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title class_">HasLength</span>&gt;(<span class="attr">arg</span>: T): T &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(arg.<span class="property">length</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> arg;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">logLength</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;hello&#x27;</span>);     <span class="comment">// OK</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">logLength</span>([<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>]);   <span class="comment">// OK</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">logLength</span>(&#123; <span class="attr">length</span>: <span class="number">5</span> &#125;); <span class="comment">// OK</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="条件类型"><a href="#条件类型" class="headerlink" title="条件类型"></a>条件类型</h2><p>根据条件选择类型：</p><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">IsArray</span>&lt;T&gt; = T <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="built_in">any</span>[] ? <span class="literal">true</span> : <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> A = <span class="title class_">IsArray</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">string</span>[]&gt;;  <span class="comment">// true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> B = <span class="title class_">IsArray</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">number</span>&gt;;    <span class="comment">// false</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 提取数组元素类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">ElementOf</span>&lt;T&gt; = T <span class="title function_">extends</span> (infer E)[] ? E : <span class="built_in">never</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> C = <span class="title class_">ElementOf</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">string</span>[]&gt;;  <span class="comment">// string</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="映射类型"><a href="#映射类型" class="headerlink" title="映射类型"></a>映射类型</h2><p>批量转换类型：</p><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 所有属性变为只读</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">Readonly</span>&lt;T&gt; = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">readonly</span> [P <span class="keyword">in</span> keyof T]: T[P];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 所有属性变为可选</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">Partial</span>&lt;T&gt; = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  [P <span class="keyword">in</span> keyof T]?: T[P];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 提取字符串键</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">KeysOfType</span>&lt;T, U&gt; = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  [P <span class="keyword">in</span> keyof T]: T[P] <span class="keyword">extends</span> U ? P : <span class="built_in">never</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;[keyof T];</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="模板字面量类型"><a href="#模板字面量类型" class="headerlink" title="模板字面量类型"></a>模板字面量类型</h2><p>在类型中使用模板字符串：</p><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">EventName</span>&lt;T <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="built_in">string</span>&gt; = <span class="string">`on<span class="subst">$&#123;Capitalize&lt;T&gt;&#125;</span>`</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">ClickEvent</span> = <span class="title class_">EventName</span>&lt;<span class="string">&#x27;click&#x27;</span>&gt;;  <span class="comment">// &#x27;onClick&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">ChangeEvent</span> = <span class="title class_">EventName</span>&lt;<span class="string">&#x27;change&#x27;</span>&gt;; <span class="comment">// &#x27;onChange&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 组合多个类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">CSSUnit</span> = <span class="string">&#x27;px&#x27;</span> | <span class="string">&#x27;em&#x27;</span> | <span class="string">&#x27;rem&#x27;</span> | <span class="string">&#x27;%&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">CSSProperty</span>&lt;T <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="built_in">string</span>&gt; = <span class="string">`<span class="subst">$&#123;T&#125;</span>:<span class="subst">$&#123;<span class="built_in">number</span>&#125;</span><span class="subst">$&#123;CSSUnit&#125;</span>`</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="attr">margin</span>: <span class="title class_">CSSProperty</span>&lt;<span class="string">&#x27;margin&#x27;</span>&gt; = <span class="string">&#x27;margin:10px&#x27;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="递归类型"><a href="#递归类型" class="headerlink" title="递归类型"></a>递归类型</h2><p>处理嵌套结构：</p><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">DeepReadonly</span>&lt;T&gt; = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">readonly</span> [P <span class="keyword">in</span> keyof T]: T[P] <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="built_in">object</span> </span><br><span class="line">    ? <span class="title class_">DeepReadonly</span>&lt;T[P]&gt; </span><br><span class="line">    : T[P];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">Nested</span> = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">a</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">b</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">c</span>: <span class="built_in">number</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">Result</span> = <span class="title class_">DeepReadonly</span>&lt;<span class="title class_">Nested</span>&gt;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// &#123; readonly a: &#123; readonly b: &#123; readonly c: number &#125; &#125; &#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="工具类型实现"><a href="#工具类型实现" class="headerlink" title="工具类型实现"></a>工具类型实现</h2><p>手写 TypeScript 内置工具类型：</p><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// ReturnType</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">MyReturnType</span>&lt;T <span class="title function_">extends</span> (...<span class="attr">args</span>: <span class="built_in">any</span>) =&gt; <span class="built_in">any</span>&gt; = </span><br><span class="line">  T <span class="title function_">extends</span> (...<span class="attr">args</span>: <span class="built_in">any</span>) =&gt; infer R ? R : <span class="built_in">never</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Parameters</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">MyParameters</span>&lt;T <span class="title function_">extends</span> (...<span class="attr">args</span>: <span class="built_in">any</span>) =&gt; <span class="built_in">any</span>&gt; = </span><br><span class="line">  T <span class="title function_">extends</span> (...<span class="attr">args</span>: infer P) =&gt; <span class="built_in">any</span> ? P : <span class="built_in">never</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// NonNullable</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">MyNonNullable</span>&lt;T&gt; = T <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="literal">null</span> | <span class="literal">undefined</span> ? <span class="built_in">never</span> : T;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="分布式条件类型"><a href="#分布式条件类型" class="headerlink" title="分布式条件类型"></a>分布式条件类型</h2><p>条件类型的特殊行为：</p><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">ToArray</span>&lt;T&gt; = T <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="built_in">any</span> ? T[] : <span class="built_in">never</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">StrArrOrNumArr</span> = <span class="title class_">ToArray</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">string</span> | <span class="built_in">number</span>&gt;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 相当于: ToArray&lt;string&gt; | ToArray&lt;number&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 结果: string[] | number[]</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 使用方括号包裹阻止分发</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">ToArrayNonDist</span>&lt;T&gt; = [T] <span class="keyword">extends</span> [<span class="built_in">any</span>] ? T[] : <span class="built_in">never</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">StrAndNumArr</span> = <span class="title class_">ToArrayNonDist</span>&lt;<span class="built_in">string</span> | <span class="built_in">number</span>&gt;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 结果: (string | number)[]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="实际应用示例"><a href="#实际应用示例" class="headerlink" title="实际应用示例"></a>实际应用示例</h2><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// API 响应类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">interface</span> <span class="title class_">ApiResponse</span>&lt;T&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">data</span>: T;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">status</span>: <span class="built_in">number</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">message</span>: <span class="built_in">string</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 提取 data 类型</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">DataOf</span>&lt;T&gt; = T <span class="keyword">extends</span> &#123; <span class="attr">data</span>: infer D &#125; ? D : <span class="built_in">never</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 使用</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">UserResponse</span> = <span class="title class_">ApiResponse</span>&lt;&#123; <span class="attr">id</span>: <span class="built_in">number</span>; <span class="attr">name</span>: <span class="built_in">string</span> &#125;&gt;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">type</span> <span class="title class_">User</span> = <span class="title class_">DataOf</span>&lt;<span class="title class_">UserResponse</span>&gt;;  <span class="comment">// &#123; id: number; name: string &#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>掌握这些高级类型技巧，让你的 TypeScript 代码更加类型安全！ 💪</p>]]>
